snippet.title: 6 Hour 4K Beautiful places Aerial Views
snippet.description:
Please enjoy 6Hour aerial journey of beautiful places on the Earth.
This tour will take you around the world's great nature. 
From Islands,Forests, Mountains, Rivers and Waterfalls please enjoy no loop movie of scenic views.

If you like our video, please subscribe to our channel
http://www.youtube.com/channel/UCb57aRZr3KsykS_wNsD5Ptw?sub_confirmation=1
